headline: Despite Fast-paced Momentum, CarMax (KMX) Is Still a Bargain Stock
summary: CarMax (KMX) could be a great choice for investors looking to buy stocks that have gained strong momentum recently but are still trading at reasonable prices. It is one of the several stocks that made it through our 'Fast-Paced Momentum at a Bargain' screen.
